    dc:description "FIGURES 67–72. Gorochovgryllacris n. gen. (G. navicula navicula n. comb.). 67–68. Male habitus in lateral and dorsolateral view. 69. Male tegmina. 70–71. Male terminalia in lateral and latero-axial view respectively. 72. Female habitus in dorsal view. (Photos by Holger Braun)." ;
